00:57:46.180 --> 00:57:47.290
weird name, right?

00:57:47.290 --> 00:57:52.390
'Cause DC Comics means it's Detective Comic's
comics.

00:57:52.390 --> 00:57:53.490
That's just the way it is.

00:57:53.490 --> 00:57:58.780
DC is our oldest surviving comic book company
in America.

00:57:58.780 --> 00:58:03.650
You know, sometimes stuff from the olden days,
