00:58:19.830 --> 00:58:24.760
GENE: The question is, do I just have ideas
on my own, or do I have somebody helping me

00:58:24.760 --> 00:58:26.400
with ideas?

00:58:26.400 --> 00:58:27.830
I would say it depends on the book.

00:58:27.830 --> 00:58:33.690
So, when I'm writing for DC Comics, the stories
that I'm writing are part of a bigger universe.

00:58:33.690 --> 00:58:37.690
