01:00:49.170 --> 01:00:54.870
It felt great that somebody wanted to read
my book so much that they were willing to

01:00:54.870 --> 01:00:56.601
part with three dollar bills for it.

01:00:56.601 --> 01:00:59.310
It was awesome.

01:00:59.310 --> 01:01:06.860
Yes, young man in the front?

01:01:06.860 --> 01:01:10.940
AUDIENCE: When did you make your first comic
book?

01:01:10.940 --> 01:01:12.750
GENE: When did I make my first comic?

