01:01:32.020 --> 01:01:33.430
GENE: Do I have any more copies?

01:01:33.430 --> 01:01:38.560
I'm sure if I went back to my parents' house
and I dug around, I'd be able to find one.

01:01:38.560 --> 01:01:40.220
Yeah, of that fifth grade comic.

